1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:05,023
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:10,527
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,527 --> 00:00:16,955
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,955 --> 00:00:21,435
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,435 --> 00:00:25,883
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,883 --> 00:00:30,794
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,794 --> 00:00:34,843
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,843 --> 00:00:39,378
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,378 --> 00:00:43,675
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,675 --> 00:00:48,440
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,931
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,931 --> 00:00:55,611
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,257 --> 00:01:00,635
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,635 --> 00:01:03,136
=Episode 18=

15
00:01:04,533 --> 00:01:06,976
Then I will have to trouble you a lot

16
00:01:08,433 --> 00:01:10,240
for the matter of Lihuai International.

17
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:21,266
I've already taken care of this matter.

18
00:01:23,833 --> 00:01:26,766
The group will no longer
hold you accountable,

19
00:01:28,366 --> 00:01:30,599
and you're done with it.

20
00:01:32,166 --> 00:01:36,333
Things got a little out of hand for me,

21
00:01:37,033 --> 00:01:39,699
but our goal
has been basically achieved.

22
00:01:40,466 --> 00:01:44,066
It's all Dork Jin's fault.
I can't wait to flay her.

23
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:44,900
Oh.

24
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:45,533
No.

25
00:01:45,533 --> 00:01:46,733
I just did my nails.

26
00:01:48,866 --> 00:01:52,099
Anyway, I've already given
you what you wanted.

27
00:01:52,633 --> 00:01:59,799
You guys keep a low profile from now on.
I don't want any more mistakes.

28
00:02:00,233 --> 00:02:02,766
How could that be, Mr. Li?

29
00:02:03,833 --> 00:02:06,899
Actually, we've discovered

30
00:02:07,433 --> 00:02:09,199
a big secret.

31
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,300
Hahaha.

32
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:13,533
Miss Jin

33
00:02:16,133 --> 00:02:17,566
has a younger sister.

34
00:02:27,133 --> 00:02:28,256
So what's the big deal?

35
00:02:28,256 --> 00:02:29,400
No.

36
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,933
Who doesn't have siblings?

37
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:38,333
Well,

38
00:02:38,666 --> 00:02:40,733
we've already done what we should do.

39
00:02:41,633 --> 00:02:44,899
You and Miss Gu are both so wealthy.

40
00:02:46,833 --> 00:02:48,366
I think it's best

41
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,966
we don't see each other again.

42
00:02:54,966 --> 00:02:56,866
Let's leave.

43
00:02:57,033 --> 00:02:58,266
Right, let's leave.

44
00:03:04,933 --> 00:03:06,566
Bye.

45
00:03:11,866 --> 00:03:13,666
You just let them leave like that?

46
00:03:13,733 --> 00:03:16,133
Without those four people
making trouble in the company,

47
00:03:16,633 --> 00:03:18,466
what about our plan on spying?

48
00:03:18,766 --> 00:03:21,533
Miss Gu, you don't need
to worry about this.

49
00:03:22,233 --> 00:03:25,499
Those people are of no use anymore.

50
00:03:26,033 --> 00:03:30,333
Now, I've stolen all the technology
and business resources.

51
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:38,333
Once we break their cooperation
with Lihuai, it'll collapse itself.

52
00:03:41,433 --> 00:03:46,499
Once WE Group is ruined,
Lan won't be able to leave me.

53
00:03:46,666 --> 00:03:51,520
Besides, their internal cash flow
is extremely tight now.

54
00:03:52,366 --> 00:03:56,224
It must be difficult for them to develop
new products for the new quarter.

55
00:03:56,900 --> 00:04:03,200
Most importantly, I'm fully responsible
for cooperating with Lihuai.

56
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:07,666
If I don't want to,
they can't cooperate.

57
00:04:12,352 --> 00:04:14,464
(Lan Rensha)

58
00:04:16,900 --> 00:04:18,266
I'm taking a call.

59
00:04:28,133 --> 00:04:29,999
Hello, Dad. What's up?

60
00:04:30,816 --> 00:04:33,120
Yuan, what are you doing?

61
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,800
Father, what are you talking about?

62
00:04:37,088 --> 00:04:41,066
I've been in business for over 50 years.
I can see through your tricks.

63
00:04:42,144 --> 00:04:44,384
But I didn't expect you
to make such a big deal.

64
00:04:44,966 --> 00:04:46,784
I gave you so many shares in the group

65
00:04:47,168 --> 00:04:49,966
to ensure you a lifetime of wealth.
Why do you still want to...?

66
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,933
Why? You just tell me.

67
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,528
Why didn't you marry my mom?

68
00:04:55,233 --> 00:04:57,440
Do you know how miserable my mom was
when she passed away?

69
00:04:58,033 --> 00:05:01,099
Did you ever come back
to see us? Did you?

70
00:05:02,066 --> 00:05:06,366
If Lan Chen's father
hadn't died in a car accident,

71
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:09,100
you might have forgotten
that you had another son.

72
00:05:09,166 --> 00:05:11,333
Believe it or not, I can make you
lose everything instantly

73
00:05:11,333 --> 00:05:12,399
and have no place to go.

74
00:05:18,366 --> 00:05:20,256
Father, I'm sorry.

75
00:05:21,184 --> 00:05:23,584
I didn't know
it'd turn into such a big deal.

76
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:27,744
I'll assist Lan Chen well in the future.

77
00:05:28,512 --> 00:05:30,399
Swear on your mother.

78
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:42,366
I swear on my mother's reputation

79
00:05:43,333 --> 00:05:47,699
that I will assist Lan Chen well
in the development of WE Group.

80
00:05:47,766 --> 00:05:50,266
Father, are you satisfied now?

81
00:05:50,592 --> 00:05:51,296
Humph.

82
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:57,366
I swear I will bring down WE Group

83
00:05:57,400 --> 00:06:00,300
by whatever means.

84
00:06:05,233 --> 00:06:07,232
What's got you so worked up, Yuan?

85
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:11,166
It's nothing, just my family business.

86
00:06:11,666 --> 00:06:12,566
Family business?

87
00:06:15,233 --> 00:06:18,333
Speaking of which,
you still haven't started a family.

88
00:06:20,033 --> 00:06:21,966
A man's career is of prime importance.

89
00:06:23,456 --> 00:06:27,100
But a man without love
is quite terrifying.

90
00:06:27,766 --> 00:06:30,733
Miss Gu, do you believe in love?

91
00:06:31,933 --> 00:06:32,896
You asked me?

92
00:06:34,333 --> 00:06:35,520
Of course, I do.

93
00:06:37,766 --> 00:06:41,666
But the person I love,

94
00:06:44,566 --> 00:06:46,533
the one who grew up with me

95
00:06:49,033 --> 00:06:51,599
has always seen me as a competitor.

96
00:06:52,466 --> 00:06:54,699
So you want to ruin him, right?

97
00:06:57,466 --> 00:06:58,720
I'm not like you.

98
00:06:59,966 --> 00:07:01,566
I have only one goal,

99
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:05,400
that is to make him completely mine.

100
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:09,066
Whether it's reaching
the summit with him

101
00:07:09,866 --> 00:07:10,766
or

102
00:07:12,133 --> 00:07:13,199
ruining him.

103
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:17,566
Miss Gu, you're quite contradictory.

104
00:07:19,766 --> 00:07:21,999
I can't help it. I'm stupid in love.

105
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:37,056
(Lan Chen)

106
00:07:42,966 --> 00:07:43,999
Yuan is not answering.

107
00:07:44,166 --> 00:07:45,466
Let's sort it out ourselves first then.

108
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:49,333
Why didn't you sort out these bills
a long time ago?

109
00:07:51,033 --> 00:07:53,566
Because although our group
has grown very big,

110
00:07:53,966 --> 00:07:56,666
all our funding comes from our family.

111
00:07:56,733 --> 00:07:59,066
There's no need to check
the bills as we're not listed,

112
00:07:59,566 --> 00:08:01,166
and the family
didn't pay much attention to it.

113
00:08:01,733 --> 00:08:04,233
But that doesn't mean
you shouldn't know.

114
00:08:04,533 --> 00:08:07,699
There are some things
you'd better not know.

115
00:08:09,766 --> 00:08:12,399
So you knew about this
from the beginning?

116
00:08:13,133 --> 00:08:14,299
You used this opportunity

117
00:08:14,366 --> 00:08:16,566
to eliminate all the enemies
in the company at once.

118
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:22,200
Do you remember I told you
they were all at the heart of the group

119
00:08:22,933 --> 00:08:24,224
when you gave me the design draft?

120
00:08:25,248 --> 00:08:27,616
They were deeply rooted here
before I took over the company.

121
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:31,933
If I had got rid of them recklessly,

122
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,933
the group could have faced
major issues at any time.

123
00:08:34,033 --> 00:08:37,056
So we need an opportunity.

124
00:08:37,766 --> 00:08:40,700
Anyway, I am warning you again.

125
00:08:40,766 --> 00:08:43,166
If you treat me as a pawn,

126
00:08:43,266 --> 00:08:46,000
I will surely drag you down with me.

127
00:08:48,333 --> 00:08:53,000
That would be the most romantic thing.

128
00:08:54,066 --> 00:08:56,966
I really hate this disgusting
and narcissistic side of you.

129
00:09:19,666 --> 00:09:20,416
Miss Jin,

130
00:09:21,966 --> 00:09:22,966
what do you think

131
00:09:25,333 --> 00:09:27,799
about Zeng Huaishi?

132
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:34,866
He is mature and stable
and gives a sense of security.

133
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:38,266
So whether as a business partner
or a husband,

134
00:09:38,333 --> 00:09:39,733
he's the best choice.

135
00:09:48,833 --> 00:09:50,366
You like him for his money, don't you?

136
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,333
I didn't expect you
to be this kind of person.

137
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:56,133
Money is great. Of course I like it.

138
00:09:56,933 --> 00:10:00,066
Besides, you're loaded too.

139
00:10:00,133 --> 00:10:01,833
But I'm not fond of you.

140
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:02,700
Right,

141
00:10:02,900 --> 00:10:03,700
Mr. Lan?

142
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:12,366
Money isn't everything.
Character is important.

143
00:10:17,133 --> 00:10:17,933
Miss Jin.

144
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,033
Could you

145
00:10:24,266 --> 00:10:25,666
possibly not like Zeng Huaishi?

146
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,120
I...

147
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:31,333
It's

148
00:10:31,933 --> 00:10:32,899
none of your business.

149
00:10:39,066 --> 00:10:39,866
Miss Jin, I...

150
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:42,933
There's a big problem

151
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,366
with Mr. Li's bills.

152
00:10:48,166 --> 00:10:49,266
Come in.

153
00:10:57,433 --> 00:10:59,933
- Mr. Lan.
- Everything's been handled.

154
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,200
Aren't these four...?

155
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:06,500
Yes, they were the assistants
of the previous directors.

156
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:10,433
So you had them placed
by their sides a long time ago?

157
00:11:10,533 --> 00:11:12,466
They are now heads
of their respective departments

158
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:14,333
and can quickly take over the work,

159
00:11:14,433 --> 00:11:16,699
so it will not be affected.

160
00:11:18,666 --> 00:11:21,433
So they have already mastered
all the skills.

161
00:11:21,433 --> 00:11:23,399
They know the process
and can get back the resources.

162
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:23,800
Yes.

163
00:11:25,166 --> 00:11:27,166
These are questionable bills.

164
00:11:28,766 --> 00:11:29,733
Are we investigating Mr. Li?

165
00:11:32,866 --> 00:11:35,899
I think Yuan might have been fooled
into signing these,

166
00:11:36,533 --> 00:11:39,333
but it doesn't rule out his suspicion.

167
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:44,933
But he owns many shares in the company.
He wouldn't hurt his own interests.

168
00:11:46,633 --> 00:11:49,366
Miss Jin, remember it.

169
00:11:49,366 --> 00:11:52,799
Always trust but verify in business.

170
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:55,800
Mr. Lan,

171
00:11:56,066 --> 00:11:59,133
our current working capital
isn't enough anymore.

172
00:11:59,133 --> 00:12:01,066
Lay off all the people
in the R&D department.

173
00:12:02,033 --> 00:12:04,666
By the way, make sure
they get sufficient severance pay.

174
00:12:05,866 --> 00:12:09,766
Although the new products developed
in the last two years are not so good...

175
00:12:09,766 --> 00:12:12,066
It's okay. I will take care of it.

176
00:12:14,266 --> 00:12:17,216
You're so ruthless, Mr. Lan.
I've finally experienced it.

177
00:12:18,933 --> 00:12:19,733
What?

178
00:12:21,166 --> 00:12:23,333
I've been working hard
for checking bills,

179
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,900
and paying any price,

180
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,266
but you still don't give me
all your trust.

181
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:29,066
Are you going to fire me
after finishing using me?

182
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,200
Miss Jin,

183
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,933
I didn't treat you as a pawn.

184
00:12:32,033 --> 00:12:32,866
I just...

185
00:12:37,933 --> 00:12:38,733
I'm okay.

186
00:12:40,433 --> 00:12:42,592
Get the car ready. I'm going home now.

187
00:12:43,533 --> 00:12:44,499
Going home now?

188
00:12:44,533 --> 00:12:45,933
Yes, with Miss Jin.

189
00:13:00,033 --> 00:13:02,799
Young Master, the guests
have been waiting for a long time.

190
00:13:03,433 --> 00:13:04,599
Why did you bring me here?

191
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:08,500
We need a top-tier designer
from across the country

192
00:13:08,633 --> 00:13:09,799
to help us develop new products.

193
00:13:09,966 --> 00:13:11,266
Why not at the office?

194
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,433
She prefers talking at my house.

195
00:13:42,932 --> 00:13:47,454
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

196
00:13:50,484 --> 00:13:55,445
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

197
00:13:58,494 --> 00:14:04,318
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

198
00:14:04,318 --> 00:14:10,880
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

199
00:14:11,424 --> 00:14:15,269
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

200
00:14:15,269 --> 00:14:19,390
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

201
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:21,086
♪Open my secret♪

202
00:14:21,086 --> 00:14:27,134
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

203
00:14:27,134 --> 00:14:31,006
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

204
00:14:31,006 --> 00:14:35,512
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

205
00:14:37,472 --> 00:14:44,222
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
